Gnoland testnet 2 CREATE USERNAME , 250 gnot e suficient - ii aduni din airdrop si cumulezi pe o singura adresa Open Ubuntu tastezi cd ./gno make Generate a seed/mnemonic code. ./build/gnokey generate Create new account cu mnemonic, inlocuiesti KEYNAME ( cheie de identificare, ) ./build/gnokey add KEYNAME --recover Bagi o parola,repeti parola, paste mnemonic phrases Verifici contul, vei vedea mai multe adrese ,copy address - aia pe care ai schimbat-o KEYNAME ./build/gnokey list Mergi la faucet https://test2.gno.land/faucet ,primesti extrem de putin ,e musai sa "umbli" la ce ai primit din airdrop,muti 250 gnot in testnet wallet Get your current balance, account number, and sequence number. Inlocuiesti ACCOUNT_ADDR cu adresa ta ./build/gnokey query auth/accounts/ACCOUNT_ADDR --remote test2.gno.land:36657 Register username Inlocuiesti ADDRESS si USERNAME gnokey maketx call ADDRESS --pkgpath "gno.land/r/users" --func "Register" --gas-fee 1000000ugnot --gas-wanted 2000000 --send "200000000ugnot" --broadcast true --chainid "test2" --args "" --args "USERNAME" --args "" --remote "test2.gno.land:36657" ✅ 🔜 next steps\!
